v4W.ENko - "IAM-08_CPP-05_S-36".
[Intermediate Algorithmic Multicomponent]
[COLOR Practice with Patterns] [Statics] 
Background color domination [slow color side] - Black
The "Main Crystal" is multicolored. The matrix is fragmented. 
The artwork connects intermediate cross-pattern`s instructions to demonstrate the multicomponent relationship of various geometric algorithms. The abstraction is dedicated to the "Metaball", "Voronoi diagram" and "Delaunay triangulation" transformations. The patterns are linked in specific way to draw the algorithmic abstract artwork with each other. The energy of abstract processes in relationship of algorithms is linked inside. The whole visualizations is forming the abstract static image. The pool of colors is forming the maximum visual shower.
